OL,3,CMan taken to hospital after falling
OL,4,Cfrom roof in Leicester
OL,6,FA man has been taken to hospital after
OL,7,Ffalling from a roof in Leicester.
OL,9,FPolice said they received a call at
OL,10,F1.17am on Sunday, April 19, after
OL,11,Freports of a break-in at a property in
OL,12,FTudor Road.
OL,14,FOfficers were also told the same man
OL,15,Fwas attempting to gain access to
OL,16,Fanother property in the street.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
