OL,3,CMan taken to hospital after falling
OL,4,Cfrom roof in Leicester
OL,6,FLeicestershire Police said officers
OL,7,Farrived at the scene to find the man
OL,8,Fon the roof of a property. Officers
OL,9,Fattempted to engage with the man for
OL,10,Fseveral minutes before he fell from
OL,11,Fthe roof, police added.
OL,13,FAs a result of the fall, the man
OL,14,Fsustained injuries to his arm and
OL,15,Fcurrently remains in hospital
OL,16,Freceiving treatment.
OL,18,FA cordon was put in place in Tudor
OL,19,FRoad this morning, with part of the
OL,20,Fstreet closed off while officers
OL,21,Fcarried out enquiries at the scene.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
