OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1776687066
OL,3,CMan taken to hospital after falling
OL,4,Cfrom roof in Leicester
OL,6,FPolice said the investigation remains
OL,7,Fat an early stage. No arrests have
OL,8,Fbeen made.
OL,10,FA mandatory referral has been made to
OL,11,Fthe Independent Office for Police
OL,12,FConduct (IOPC) due to police contact
OL,13,Fwith the man.
OL,15,FAnyone with information should contact
OL,16,FLeicestershire Police on 101, quoting
OL,17,Fincident 49 of April 19.
